<br>
Well, I just wanted to let everyone know what a wonderful person whoever the original owner is.  Around the first of the year he GANKED THE ACCOUNT BACK.  Now, this wonderful piece of shit has put the account up for sale on Playerauctions (Item# 1049067670)   He has several other accounts up for sale under the username of rallostrader.<br>
<br>
About a month ago, I saw this Telaize guilded in Reverant along with a character named Couven (wizard I think).  Now, considering that Telaize's name had been changed from Couver, it would seem these 2 characters were probably the same people.  Reverant really recruits some quality people.<br>
<br>
Anyways, my whole point of posting this is to give anyone looking to buy an account fair warning against this guy and let people know what kind of people Reverant recruits.  Enjoy!<br>
